data.description: Welcome to the peaceful Oak Lake neighborhood! The open foyer will invite guests into this gorgeous home with a formal dining room to the left and a seating area/in home office to the right. Through the entry is the living area w/ gas fireplace & built in wet bar. Enjoy the views of a fully fenced backyard from the attached kitchen island in this open concept kitchen & breakfast nook and enjoy all of the natural sunlight flooding into the sunroom overlooking the yard and deck. The primary bedroom boasts an attached sitting area or could be converted into a 5th room, with the jetted tub in the primary bath, tiled shower stall, vanity and walk in closet, all flowing in this large space. The additional guest rooms offer ample space & nicely proportioned closet space.
